Bulding bsod-client:
----------------------------------
----------------------------------

Linux:
----------------------------------

Install:
 * SDL_net-dev
 * zlib-dev
 * libpng-dev
 * devil-dev
 * libconfig

Build bsod-client:
 * make

Configure bsod-client:
 * vi bsod.conf

Run:
 * ./runbsod.sh


Windows
----------------------------------

Install:
 * libsdl-dev
 * devil-dev
 * libconfig

Configure bsod-client:
 * edit bsod.conf

Run:
 * bsod.exe
